Package: ai.vital.vitalsigns.classloader

[Java] Class VitalSignsRootClassLoader

          • ai.vital.vitalsigns.classloader.VitalSignsRootClassLoader

          • A class loader that may loads classes from both classpath or jimfs instance. May be set as a root classloader
